	dprr:hasNoteText "Praetor (Oros. 5.21.10) under the command of Papirius Carbo (App. BC 1.87). He was defeated by Metellus on the Aesis in Umbria, and at Spoletium by Pompey and Licinius Crassus, then, escaping from Spoletium, he" ;
	dprr:hasID 4141 .
